      <p>The blocks available in <uicontrol>FORM BUSINESS LOGIC</uicontrol> and  <uicontrol>LIST PAGE BUSINESS LOGIC</uicontrol> are same except for the <uicontrol>ACTIONS</uicontrol> block. The <uicontrol>ACTIONS</uicontrol> block is the final output of the business logic that you must configure once you navigate to the list page. For more information on other blocks, refer to <xref href="Blocks.xml"/>.</p>
      <p>The following table provides information on the blocks available in the <uicontrol>ACTIONS</uicontrol> block:<table>
